Package atst.giss.abplc

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IABPlcioConnection
    The common interface of all Allen-Bradley PLC Connections used by the GISS to communicate with the GIS PLC.
    IABPlcioConnectionGis
    Interface of the Allen-Bradley PLC Connection used by GIS Equipment controller atst.giss.
    IABPlcioMaster
    IABPlcioMaster is the public interface to the Allen-Bradley PLCIO Master.
    IPlcioCall
    Interface describing PlcioCall objects used to pass PLCIO function call information to the ABPlcioMaster.
    IPlcioPcFormatType
    Interface describing PLCIO pcFormat strings as represented by objects of type PlcioPcFormatType.
    IPlcTag
    The public interface containing constants and methods used to operate with PlcTag objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ABPlcioChannel
    This is the GISS channel class used by the ABPlcioConnection class to read and write PLC tags to the GIS PLC.
    ABPlcioConnection
    This is the GISS abstract connection class from which all GISS controller specific connection classes are derived.
    ABPlcioConnectionGis
    This is the GISS connection class used by GIS controller atst.giss to communicate with the GIS PLC.
    ABPlcioExceptionJNI
    Class containing the exception thrown when unable to communicate with the GIS PLC due to a JNI error.
    ABPlcioExceptionPLCIO
    Class containing the exception thrown when unable to communicate with the GIS PLC due to a PLCIO error.
    ABPlcioMaster
    ABPlcioMaster is the class that handles all Allen-Bradley PLC communication using the PLCIO C library.
    GisToGissIcdConstants
    The constants for items needed between the GIS and GISS.
    PlcioCall
    Class providing behavior required to pass PLCIO function call information to the ABPlcioMaster#plcAccess(IPlcioCall) method.
    PlcioPcFormat
    The abstract class PlcioPcFormat contains constants and helper methods used when operating with PLCIO pcFormat strings.
    PlcioPcFormatTestHarness
    Use and output:
    PlcTag
    The class PlcTag describes an Allen-Bradley PLC tag and stores its values in the Cache.
    PlcTagReader
    This class is used to read a specific PLC tag at a specified interval.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ABPlcioExceptionPLCIO.PlcioErrorCode
    Enumeration of PLCIO error codes returned when call to PLCIO function fails.
    IPlcioCall.PlcioMethodName
    Enumeration of all PLCIO function calls recognized and used by the GISS.
    IPlcTag.PropTypes
    Enumeration representing the propertyDB types used by GIS PLC tag items.
    IPlcTag.TagItemMetadataIndex
    Enumeration describing the contents of a tag item's propertyDB attribute IPlcTag#TAG_METADATA value.
    IPlcTag.TagMetadataIndex
    Enumeration describing the contents of the tag's propertyDB attribute IPlcTag#TAG_METADATA value.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ABPlcioExceptionBadPlcTagProperties
    Class containing the exception thrown when the propertyDB attributes describing a PLC tag cannot be used to successfully create or work with a PlcTag object.
